		<Function ID="165" Name="Conditional Copy_2000DTP0250_Member Level Dates" Template="ConditionalCopy">
			<Properties Category="BusinessGroups">
				<Property Name="BGSet">13</Property>
			</Properties>
			<Properties Category="GlobalUserNotes">
				<Property Name="{1c5b61ef-44fa-4a32-aefb-e846cf85cbed}">In this condition copy first we are cheacking the transaction is Ammend/Create/terminate.
If it is ammend we are cheacking DTP under ST segment,DTP01=303 if it is true then we map DTP03 to asofdate.
And DTP01!=303,We are cheacking DTP01=007 if it is true then we map DTP03 to Asofdate.


If it is Terminate we are cheacking DTP under 2000 loop,DTP01=357 then we are mapping DTP03 to Asofdate.
And if DTP01!=357,
we are cheacking DTP under 2200and 2300 wheather they equal to DTP*349.
 if it is equal then map corresponding DTP03 to Asofdate</Property>
			</Properties>
			<Properties Category="Settings">
				<Property Name="if_1/conditions/expression_1/arg1">1</Property>
				<Property Name="if_1/conditions/expression_1/arg1/type">1</Property>
